<div tiddler="AuthorMode" modifier="BraddeGraf" modified="200606281940" created="200606281925" tags="how-to">Your file is in author mode if it's on your local harddrive. All of the authoring tools are visible for you to work on the document.\n\nWhen you publish the file to a web server, it automatically goes to PublishMode, which hides the authoring tools so as to not confuse your audience.</div>